      <section eId="sec_CCP-2168">
        <num>CCP 2168</num>
        <heading>2168. Â Posting of unpublished opinions; citation</heading>
        <subsection eId="CCP-2168__subsec_A">
          <num>A.</num>
          <content>
            <p>The unpublished opinions of the supreme court and the courts of appeal shall be posted by such courts on the Internet websites of such courts.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CCP-2168__subsec_B">
          <num>B.</num>
          <content>
            <p>Opinions posted as required in this Article may be cited as authority and, if cited, shall be cited by use of the case name and number assigned by the posting court.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=408238</p>
        </authorialNote>
